<section class="about section-padding" aria-labelledby="AboutHeading">
  <div class="container--narrow container">
    <span class="eyebrow">{{ section.settings.eyebrow | default: 'Our story' }}</span>
    <h1 id="AboutHeading" style="margin-bottom:8px;">{{ section.settings.heading | default: 'We make pet portraits because we get it.' }}</h1>
    <p class="text-muted" style="margin-bottom:40px;max-width:560px;">{{ section.settings.intro | default: 'They are family. And family belongs on the wall.' }}</p>

    <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:32px;font-size:var(--text-base);line-height:var(--leading-loose);color:var(--color-ink);">
      <div>
        <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:var(--text-lg);margin-bottom:8px;">How this started</h3>
        <p>We wanted something better than a phone photo in a frame. Something that felt like art — the kind of piece you hang in the living room and actually smile at every day. We couldn't find it, so we built it.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:var(--text-lg);margin-bottom:8px;">What we do</h3>
        <p>You upload a photo and choose from 8 artistic styles — watercolour, line art, modern shapes, pop art and more. Every detail is pulled from your actual pet, not a template. You see it before you pay. If you love it, we print it on museum-grade canvas or heavyweight paper and ship it to your door.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:var(--text-lg);margin-bottom:8px;">What we care about</h3>
        <p>Getting the eyes right. Making it feel like them. A lot of our orders are gifts — birthday presents, gotcha day surprises, memorial keepsakes. We know these pieces matter, and we treat every order that way.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-heading);font-size:var(--text-lg);margin-bottom:8px;">Who you're talking to</h3>
        <p>Small team, based in Vancouver, BC. We ship across Canada — US shipping is on the way. If something goes wrong with your order, you're talking to a real person — not a bot.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top:48px;text-align:center;">
      <a href="/pages/create" class="btn btn--primary btn--large">Create a portrait</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "About Page",
  "settings": [
    { "type": "text", "id": "eyebrow", "label": "Eyebrow", "default": "Our story" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "heading", "label": "Heading", "default": "We make pet portraits because we get it." },
    { "type": "text", "id": "intro", "label": "Intro line", "default": "They are family. And family belongs on the wall." }
  ],
  "presets": [{ "name": "About Page" }]
}
{% endschema %}
